headline: CDW Q2 Deep Dive: Diversified Portfolio and Services Investments Shape Results Amid Market Uncertainty
summary: IT solutions provider CDW (NASDAQGS:CDW) reported Q2 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 10.2% year on year to $5.98 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.60 per share was 4.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
